There is no information available for this species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="FC8E653B8749B1131B03530BFDABFA77" pageId="6" pageNumber="199" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="B42B36B08749B1131B03530BFDABFA77" blockId="6.[87,1295,281,1498]" pageId="6" pageNumber="199">
<emphasis id="86E0EAA28749B1131B03530BFE22FAC7" bold="true" box="[90,438,1305,1338]" pageId="6" pageNumber="199">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Andean distribution of the Southern Spiny Pocket Mouse has suffered habitat destruction and fragmentation due to logging.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
